3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the problem of retrieving associated subsequences from a dataset of sequences, which is a problem related to data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with a problem related to discrete sequences and their associated subsequences.
